    "15 Loss and accuracy line plots for a generative adversarial network with convergence failure owing to aggressive optimization 4.4Inception Score (IS) is a metric that accurately depicts the photographs' quality and diversity.",
    "The Inception Score evaluates the quality and diversity of produced samples.",
    "It use the Inception v3 neural network to calculate the conditional entropy of class predictions for produced data.",
    "A higher Inception Score suggests superior quality and diversity.Formula: IS = exp(Ex [D KL (p(y|x)||p(y))]) where, p(y|x) is the class distribution given a produced sample, p(y) is the marginal class distribution, and D KL represents the Kullback-Leibler divergence. 5.",
    "Fréchet Inception Distance (FID) is a metric that not only evaluates the produced pictures on their own, but also compares the genuine and false versions of an image."
